snippet.title: Ultimate Sackboy - Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
RUN races, DODGE obstacles and WIN prizes!
Unleash your imagination in Ultimate Sackboy!

Complete aesthetic race tracks and earn rewards!

★Dash, slide, and jump!
★Pick up Powerups!
★Collect bubbles and unlock new costumes!
★Enjoy colorful and vibrant HD graphics!
★Duel enemies and complete missions!
★Customize with hundreds of costume choices!

Become the Ultimate Sackboy champion!

Sackboy, LittleBigPlanet, Ultimate Sackboy (C) Sony Interactive Entertainment
Developed by Exient
Also released on iOS

#theforeseenarcade #android #androidgameplay #androidgames #sackboy #ultimatesackboy #playstation #lbp #littlebigplanet #exient

FUN FACT: It's not the first time Sackboy made his way to mobile devices. First was as part of a Karting themed minigame from PlayStation All-Stars Island (an advergame to promote Coca-Cola Zero) and later in 2014 we got Run Sackboy! Run!, developed by Firesprite (which is formed by former Psygnosis / Studio Liverpool staff).
